article.description: — Nate Johnson scored 24 points and Xavier easily handled Central Michigan 78-45 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Johnson scores 24 to carry Xavier past C. Michigan 78-45
article.linkText: Johnson scores 24 to carry Xavier past C. Michigan 78-45
article.story: CINCINNATI -- — Nate Johnson scored 24 points and Xavier easily handled Central Michigan 78-45 on Wednesday night. Jack Nunge had 10 points, seven rebounds and three blocks for Xavier (6-1), which earned its fifth consecutive home victory. Colby Jones distributed seven assists in the win. Oscar Lopez Jr. scored 11 points with six rebounds for the Chippewas (1-6), who now have dropped four straight. Ralph Bissainthe grabbed eight rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
